_:Nbae3658f17264481a3c3a6aa22723d5b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Becky Edwards joined the Further Education (FE) Commissioner team in 2020 as an FE Adviser. She was appointed Deputy FE Commissioner in September 2023.</p>\n\n<p>She is a qualified accountant and has a master’s degree in financial management.</p>\n\n<p>She has worked in senior finance roles in the FE sector for over 25 years, including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Executive Director of Finance, City of Bristol College</li>\n  <li>Executive Director of Finance, Strode College</li>\n</ul>\n" .
